Package ca.ualberta.cmput301f18t11.medicam.models

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BodyLocation
    Attachment that represents the afflicted body part associated with the Record that holds this Attachment
    CareProvider
    Represents a careprovider user account that holds a list of patients that are tracked by/assigned to this careprovider.
    CareProviderRecord
    A basic extension of the Record object that simply attributes the record to a specified CareProvider object by that care provider's uuid.
    InstancePhoto
    A object that holds a Uri and a Bitmap to represent a photo that is to be attached to a Record object.
    LocationAttachment  
    Patient
    Represents a patient that uses this app to record their various medical problems.
    PatientRecord
    A extension of the Record class that allows a patient to record and track an affliction over time.
    Problem
    Model for a problem that tracks an affliction that a patient wants to document.
    ReferencePhoto
    A front facing or back facing full body photo meant to be attached to Problem object that can be set by a patient.
